<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_R&B_Instrumental_Performance" title="Grammy Award for Best R&amp;B Instrumental Performance">Best R&amp;B Instrumental Performance</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="Herbie_Hancock" title="Herbie Hancock">Herbie Hancock</a> for "Rockit"</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_R&B_Song" title="Grammy Award for Best R&amp;B Song">Best Rhythm &amp; Blues Song</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="Michael_Jackson" title="Michael Jackson">Michael Jackson</a> (songwriter) for "<a href="Billie_Jean" title="Billie Jean">Billie Jean</a>"</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=1984_Grammy_Awards&action=edit&section=20.php.html" title="Edit section: Rock">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Rock">Rock</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Female_Rock_Vocal_Performance" title="Grammy Award for Best Female Rock Vocal Performance">Best Rock Vocal Performance, Female</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="Pat_Benatar" title="Pat Benatar">Pat Benatar</a> for "Love Is a Battlefield"</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Male_Rock_Vocal_Performance" title="Grammy Award for Best Male Rock Vocal Performance">Best Rock Vocal Performance, Male</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="Michael_Jackson" title="Michael Jackson">Michael Jackson</a> for "<a href="Beat_It" title="Beat It">Beat It</a>"</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Rock_Performance_by_a_Duo_or_Group_with_Vocal" title="Grammy Award for Best Rock Performance by a Duo or Group with Vocal">Best Rock Performance by a Duo or Group with Vocal</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="The_Police" title="The Police">The Police</a> for <i><a href="Synchronicity_(The_Police_album)" title="Synchronicity (The Police album)">Synchronicity</a></i></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Rock_Instrumental_Performance" title="Grammy Award for Best Rock Instrumental Performance">Best Rock Instrumental Performance</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="Sting_(musician)" title="Sting (musician)">Sting</a> for "Brimstone and Treacle"</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=1984_Grammy_Awards&action=edit&section=21.php.html" title="Edit section: Spoken">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Spoken">Spoken</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Spoken_Word_Album" title="Grammy Award for Best Spoken Word Album">Best Spoken Word or Non-musical Recording</a>
<ul>
<li><a href="William_Warfield" title="William Warfield">William Warfield</a> for <i>Copland: A Lincoln Portrait</i></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
